<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row align-items-center mb-5">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold text-primary mb-4">À propos de <%= settings.site_name || 'OLM SUYARI' %></h1>
            <p class="lead">We believe that beauty is not just about looking good, it's about feeling confident and empowered in your own skin.</p>
            <p class="text-muted mb-4">Founded in 2026, OLM SUYARI emerged from a desire to create premium, luxury beauty products accessible to everyone. Our products are carefully crafted using the finest ingredients to enhance your natural glow.</p>
            <a href="/shop" class="btn btn-primary rounded-pill px-4">Shop Our Collection</a>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1596462502278-27bfdc403348?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="About OLM SUYARI" class="img-fluid rounded shadow">
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row g-4 text-center mt-5">
        <h2 class="mb-4">Our Values</h2>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm py-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <i class="fas fa-leaf fa-3x text-primary mb-3"></i>
                    <h4 class="card-title">Clean Beauty</h4>
                    <p class="card-text text-muted">We prioritize ethically sourced, clean ingredients that are kind to your skin and the environment.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm py-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <i class="fas fa-gem fa-3x text-primary mb-3"></i>
                    <h4 class="card-title">Luxury Feel</h4>
                    <p class="card-text text-muted">Every product is designed to provide a premium experience, from packaging to application.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm py-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <i class="fas fa-users fa-3x text-primary mb-3"></i>
                    <h4 class="card-title">Inclusivity</h4>
                    <p class="card-text text-muted">Beauty is for everyone. We develop shades and formulas to suit a wide spectrum of skin tones.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
